<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Confirmar email - {{appName}}</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f7f8fa; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #111827;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="padding: 24px 12px;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="max-width: 560px; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px;">
            <tr>
              <td>
                <h1 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.2;">{{appName}}</h1>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 16px;">Olá, {{userName}}!</p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
                  Recebemos uma solicitação para confirmar o email <strong>{{email}}</strong> na sua conta.
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 20px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
                  Clique no botão abaixo para concluir a confirmação:
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 20px;">
                  <a href="{{confirmUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #2563eb; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600;">
                    Confirmar email
                  </a>
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">
                  Se o botão não funcionar, copie e cole este link no navegador:
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 20px; font-size: 13px; word-break: break-all;">
                  <a href="{{confirmUrl}}" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: underline;">{{confirmUrl}}</a>
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">
                  Este link expira em 30 minutos.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
